{"tid":1350382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師會稱正嚴正檢視對律師何君堯相關投訴","createTime":"2019-07-22T12:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:49:23.000Z","uid":29675,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc3569cc99b4532682955ace6170a0f4ae4d511d","tid":1350382,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:46:03.000Z","msg":"律師會表示，已收到對律師何君堯的投訴，正嚴正檢視相關投訴事件，如有需要會交予律師紀律審裁組處理，由於專業操守調查屬於保密，律師會暫時不作評論。<br />\n<br />\n公民黨前主席余若薇表示，已向律師會執業操守組投訴，要求盡快調查何君堯，懷疑他和元朗毆打事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n余若薇在社交平台表示互聯網流傳片段，可見酷似何君堯的人答謝懷疑毆打市民的人士，懷疑何君堯涉嫌違反《律師執業規則》。"},{"pid":"2af1e239663617f1e5cd8f2683ac0ae4380d536e","tid":1350382,"uid":34415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/520eo1h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F520eo1h.jpg&h=32ecfa79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbASUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbASUF.jpg&h=a2ce6deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kjPbreK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkjPbreK.jpg&h=068b8664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKrX6eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKrX6eR.jpg&h=922f47ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87OcaGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87OcaGA.jpg&h=5d1b1e66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6e2e88f32f97ff81a2dc4483e9b67669ed7e501","tid":1350382,"uid":132941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> strike off"},{"pid":"21a0480a4319e4d2408c5dfd13f5ae75a7c24721","tid":1350382,"uid":33848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T12